---
title: Homemade Cheeseburger Beef Pizza with Fresh Dough, Cheddar & Pickled Onion
description: Two takeaway favourites in one meal? Sounds like heaven to us. Cheeseburgers and pizza collide in this flavour-packed dish which will surely have your mouth watering. A crisp pizza base is topped with juicy beef, pickled onions, and burger sauce. And for the ultimate finishing touch, a sprinkling of sesame seeds around the crust give the perfect burger-style flair!
